{"tid":1039373,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"政府200幾億買物業 領展好可疑","createTime":"2019-02-27T11:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T11:10:45.000Z","uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e50b74a7fb3fa291afad04f28163a1ffd56e793","tid":1039373,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"今日財政預算案，提到撥款200億，購置60個物業，以供設立超過130項社福設施，包括日間幼兒中心、長者鄰舍中心、到校學前康復服務等，預計約86000人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n睇返「最有嫌疑」的領展，於本港有138個物業，當中迄今完成的資產提升項目總共71項，於香港訂立租約超過9300份。<br />\n<br />\n要市區物業有市區物業，的確係同領展傾一炮過，點都快過要「又傾又砌」，要收集業權。<br />\n<br />\n市區物業，同大孖沙傾，隨時又被批評勾結，不如同「自己人」傾。<br />\n<br />\n問題一：<br />\n<br />\n如果真係問領展買，算唔算「另類回購」呢？完大家一個心願？<br />\n<br />\n問題二：<br />\n<br />\n如果政府真係買，又做唔做到香港大業主呢？<br />\n<br />\n答案係做唔到嘅，因為138-60＝78，領展就算真係賣，都仲大把貨。<br />\n<br />\n問題三：<br />\n<br />\n領展近年方向係做好管理，如果真係賣俾政府，其實收管理費會唔會仲有肉食？<br />\n<br />\n問題四：<br />\n<br />\n以資產價格來說，常說本港物業已到頂，其實對領展來說，如果真有其事，會不會是一場good deal？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/diHRZgMPw00C8ZSno6Fj_w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY2Ny42MDc4NDMxMzcyNTQ5/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/GiyRwhY.TRiPCiT1h7M2eQ--~B/aD0xNTk2O3c9MTUzMDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/b8521e760aaa73ae7a3bf356c5df629f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdiHRZgMPw00C8ZSno6Fj_w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY2Ny42MDc4NDMxMzcyNTQ5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGiyRwhY.TRiPCiT1h7M2eQ--~B%2FaD0xNTk2O3c9MTUzMDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fb8521e760aaa73ae7a3bf356c5df629f&h=cc8c0e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返現時領展物業組合，佔面積百分比係以飲食為主，佔28.8%，其次係超市17.8%，服務業只佔10.1%（租金百分比10.7%），至於其他類包括百貨、文具店、報攤一類，就佔到23.1%。<br />\n<br />\n筆者估計，如果真係要搵領展，以不得罪超市為大原則，被犧牲的相信就是其他類的那些小店吧～～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C200%E5%B9%BE%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91-073914950.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C200%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2596%2591-073914950.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=700de1c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C200%E5%B9%BE%E5%84%84%E8%B2%B7%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91-073914950.html</a>"},{"pid":"e94ca90b69478218c23e25f0151e7735b73f745d","tid":1039373,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"823 gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}